#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:1
msgid "Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel (DeepSeek-V3.1)"
msgstr "动态分块流水线并行 (DeepSeek-V3.1)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:3
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "快速入门"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:5
msgid ""
"vLLM-Ascend supports Dynamic Chunked Pipeline Parallel (CPP) for "
"optimizing prefill performance in Pipeline Parallelism scenarios. This "
"guide demonstrates deployment with DeepSeek-V3.1 on 1 Atlas 800T A3 "
"server (64G × 16)."
msgstr ""
"vLLM-Ascend 支持动态分块流水线并行 (CPP) 以优化流水线并行场景中的预填充性能。本指南演示在1台 Atlas 800T A3 "
"服务器 (64G × 16) 上使用 DeepSeek-V3.1 进行部署。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:7
#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:116
msgid ""
"For configuration details, see the [Feature "
"Guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md)."
msgstr "配置详情请参阅[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/dynamic_chunk_pipeline_parallel.md)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:9
msgid ""
"For design details, see the [Design "
"Document](../../developer_guide/Design_Documents/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)."
msgstr "设计详情请参阅[设计文档](../../developer_guide/Design_Documents/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:11
msgid "Environment Preparation"
msgstr "环境准备"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:13
msgid "Model Weight"
msgstr "模型权重"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:15
msgid "`DeepSeek-V3.1-w8a8` (Quantized version): 1 Atlas 800T A3 (64G × 16) node"
msgstr "`DeepSeek-V3.1-w8a8` (量化版本)：1个 Atlas 800T A3 (64G × 16) 节点"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:17
msgid "Download to shared directory such as `/mnt/weight/`"
msgstr "下载到共享目录，例如 `/mnt/weight/`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:19
msgid "Run with Docker"
msgstr "使用 Docker 运行"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:60
msgid "Deployment"
msgstr "部署"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:62
msgid "Startup Script"
msgstr "启动脚本"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:107
msgid "Key Parameters"
msgstr "关键参数"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:109
msgid "`--pipeline-parallel-size 2`: Enables Pipeline Parallelism (required)"
msgstr "`--pipeline-parallel-size 2`：启用流水线并行（必需）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:110
msgid "`--enable-chunked-prefill`: Enables Chunked Prefill (required)"
msgstr "`--enable-chunked-prefill`：启用分块预填充（必需）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:111
msgid ""
"`--max-num-batched-tokens 32768`: Initial chunk size (recommended for "
"128K sequences)"
msgstr "`--max-num-batched-tokens 32768`：初始分块大小（推荐用于128K序列）"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:112
msgid ""
"`profiling_chunk_config.enabled`: Enables Dynamic Chunked Pipeline "
"Parallel"
msgstr "`profiling_chunk_config.enabled`：启用动态分块流水线并行"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:113
msgid ""
"`profiling_chunk_config.smooth_factor`:  Smoothing factor (0 < x ≤ 1.0). "
"Higher values trust dynamic prediction more"
msgstr "`profiling_chunk_config.smooth_factor`：平滑因子 (0 < x ≤ 1.0)。值越大越信任动态预测"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:114
msgid ""
"`profiling_chunk_config.min_chunk`: Minimum chunk size for dynamic "
"calculation. Should be smaller than `max-num-batched-tokens`"
msgstr ""
"`profiling_chunk_config.min_chunk`：动态计算的最小分块大小。应小于 `max-num-batched-"
"tokens`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:118
msgid "Online Calibration"
msgstr "在线校准"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:120
msgid ""
"For optimal performance, online calibrate with real data before "
"production:"
msgstr "为获得最佳性能，请在投产前使用真实数据进行在线校准："

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:122
msgid ""
"You can use aisbench to generate fixed-length random datasets. Refer to "
"[Using AISBench for performance "
"evaluation](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation) for details."
msgstr ""
"您可以使用 aisbench 生成固定长度的随机数据集。详情请参阅[使用 AISBench "
"进行性能评估](../../developer_guide/evaluation/using_ais_bench.md#execute-"
"performance-evaluation)。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:124
msgid ""
"Modify "
"`<YOUR_AISBENCH_PATH>/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`:"
msgstr ""
"修改 "
"`<YOUR_AISBENCH_PATH>/benchmark/ais_bench/datasets/synthetic/synthetic_config.py`："

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:144
msgid "Run for online calibration:"
msgstr "运行在线校准："

#: ../../source/tutorials/features/dynamic_chunked_pipeline_parallel.md:150
msgid ""
"Configure online calibration data length to match your `max-model-len`. "
"Use `batch_size=1` and ensure data differs to avoid cache hits if prefix "
"caching is enabled."
msgstr "配置在线校准数据长度以匹配您的 `max-model-len`。使用 `batch_size=1` 并确保数据不同，以避免启用前缀缓存时命中缓存。"

